#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kgeography; is a geography learning tool by &kde;. Right now it has seven "
"usage modes:"
msgstr ""
"&kgeography; je &kde;-jevo orodje za učenje geografije. Trenutno ima sedem "
"načinov uporabe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Browse the maps clicking in a map division to see its name, capital and flag"
msgstr ""
"Brskajte po zemljevidih s klikom v razdelku zemljevida, da si ogledate "
"njegovo ime, glavno mesto in zastavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game tells you a map division name and you have to click on it"
msgstr "Igra pove ime dela zemljevida, na katerega morate klikniti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game tells you a capital and you have to guess the division it belongs to"
msgstr "Igra vam pove glavno mesto, vi pa morate uganiti del, ki mu pripada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game tells you a division and you have to guess its capital"
msgstr "Igra vam pove del ozemlja, vi pa morate ugibati njeno glavno mesto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game shows you a map division flag and you have to guess its name"
msgstr "Igra vam prikaže zastavo dela ozemlja, vi pa morate uganiti ime dela"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game tells you a map division name and you have to guess its flag"
msgstr "Igra vam pove ime dela ozemlja, vi pa morate uganiti zastavo tega dela"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game shows an empty map and you have to place divisions on it one by one"
msgstr ""
"Igra prikaže prazen zemljevid, vi pa morate na njem postaviti dele enega po "
"enega"

