#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then choose what type of learning or testing you want to do by "
"looking at the menu on the left:"
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko izberete, kateri način učenja ali testiranja želite preko menija "
"na levi:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
